{"tid":844063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網民發現超懷舊「錄影帶租賃店」 網民：「有無錄影機睇？」","createTime":"2018-10-01T14:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:07:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2c8f5f4c4b398a09ad57be1748b3b3f71b0846","tid":844063,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01115720/page97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F01115720%2Fpage97.jpg&h=a22db5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生長喺80年代嘅應該對「錄影帶」好有回憶，近年已經好耐無聽過呢3隻字，不過有日本網民就喺三重縣伊勢市發現呢間租借錄影帶嘅店舖，放上網後引起好大迴響。大家都話好似30年前影嘅舊相，仲形容為「古代遺跡」。租金方面，租5餅帶價錢1000円，即係10零蚊一套戲，好抵，不過租返去又有無錄影機可以睇？BTW，好多人仲話要去懷舊吓，入嚟有地址。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01115513/v4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F01115513%2Fv4.jpg&h=933dddfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameover.com.hk/日本網民發現超懷舊「錄影帶租賃店」-網民：「/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameover.com.hk%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E8%B6%85%E6%87%B7%E8%88%8A%E3%80%8C%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%B6%E7%A7%9F%E8%B3%83%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8D-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%2F&d=9MYsJ7ZD%2B279ssC7TQbG%2BBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=23d370cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameover.com.hk/日本網民發現超懷舊「錄影帶租賃店」-網民：「/</a>"},{"pid":"04db2302532423c0afe6fb69e38e1ba6dc2122df","tid":844063,"uid":26429,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"分分鍾會租到午夜凶鈴嗰餅錄影帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b373271c0a06c38d0439abcf0666f16348ba42","tid":844063,"ui